    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Traditional apparel expressing the regional, national, community, or ethnic identity of a population. Folk costume may be reserved for ceremonial events or be found in everyday use.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
